user.biography: Pro Bike Athlete and Sand Castle Builder // 📍Milton Keynes 🚲 @bulk @helfare @marinbikes

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Matt Jones in Next In Line with @van.haven. May be an image of car and outdoors.

node.text: We’ve started planning a new @van.haven build 🤓 the team there have proved that anything is achievable, from a panel van to a kitted out off-road pop top camper that will smash through rivers 💪🏼 What should we do next? 👇🏼#vanhaven

node.text: I’m so pumped to have a working set of trails at my compound. This dirt spine is preposterously steep! 😈 who’s in for a summer jam?? 🚲💨 #mtb #trails

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Matt Jones in Good To Go with @_bengrist, @mucoff, @redbulluk, @_van_haven_, and @dhb_daily. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Look at this place 😻😻😻 The compound is finally complete! What a place to ride bikes 🤩 the latest episode of the full rebuild series just went out too. Link in my bio. #mtb

Buzzing! 3 weeks ago @madmaxi37 told me how fun base jumping is… and at 4:30am today we jumped off a 220ft wind turbine 🪂 thanks so much @lemmingsbase for talking me through it 🙌🏼 #bladesofglory #givesyouwings

node.text: New setup for the airbag works like a dream. It’s mega to ride my compound again 🙌🏼🤓 I’m excited to hit the new trails for a video this weekend 🙏🏼 #mtb 🎥 @_bengrist ⛏ @dhb_daily

Riding Gorge Road Trails will always been an absolute highlight of my career. Many riders from the UK and Europe have flown to the other side of the world to hit this insane spot in NZ 🇳🇿and I always dreamed to do the same. it’s so sad to hear that the jumps are at threat of being flattened, thousands of hours of graft make this spot what it is today, it’s unreal. Head to @savegorgeroadjumps to sign the petition and we hope to keep this place open for aspiring athletes of the future! #mtb #bmx #trails

node.text: One more day of shows to go at @fosgoodwood 🙏🏼✊🏼 @helfare @samreynolds26 #mtb

I’m buzzing that @fosgoodwood is back this year! It’s been rad meeting loads of people who’ve come to watch us ride. I’m stoked to have been given the green light to get back to riding, and GoodWood will always be a super special event for me as it’s where my career with @redbull began 8 years ago, and haven’t missed a show since. #festivalofspeed
